Tim Kaine ( D - Va . ) , who [V: 's] seeking re - election , has more than $ 10 million in cash on hand going into the midterm elections , the Augusta Free Press reported . What 's the story ? During the seven - week pre - primary reporting period , Kaine reported that he raised more than $ 1.1 million , which bumped his total cash - on - hand to more than $ 10.6 million . He raked in nearly $ 200,000 through online contributions from 5,877 individual campaign donors . The senator , who 's seeking a second term after a failed vice presidential bid , held a meet and greet in New Town on Monday , where criticized President Donald Trump 's administration , The Virginia Gazette reported . He told the Memorial Day crowd that Trump seeks to divide the country . “ We ’ve got a president who is n’t ‘ for all,’ he specializes in division , ” Kaine told attendees . “ When he could n’t tell who the good guys and the bad guys were at a white supremacist rally , he ’s not ‘ for all.’ ” Kaine said his campaign is based on “ a …
